{"type": "article", "id": 34357, "title": "16年最贵的15双球鞋有这些，以及，推荐一个很特别的展览 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-11T02:32:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 34794, "name": "15双球鞋"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 14105, "name": "porter"}, {"id": 34795, "name": "wings＋horns"}, {"id": 23770, "name": "蜷川实花"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161111092207MuE2z0ZrVeDIR7OG.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/nordstrom-posts-net-loss-cites-improved-operations-10703146/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国高端百货连锁商场  Nordstrom 第三季度利润下滑</b></a> | Nordstrom 的第三季度财报显示，在去年同期 8100 万美元净收入的基础上，下滑了 1000 万美元。其中，Nordstrom 的净销售额在第三季度上涨了 7.2%，至 3.5 亿美元。由于集团内部调整，导致运营成本的增加，使得 Nordstrom 销售增长，但利润下滑。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.marketwatch.com/story/ralph-laurens-profit-slides-as-sales-fall-2016-11-10?link=MW_latest_news\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 收入大跌</b></a> | Ralph Lauren 的财报显示，截止至 10 月 1 日的过去一年中，该品牌的销售额大跌 23％，营收下降了 7.6%，至 18.2 亿美元，净利润为 4500 万美元。对于 Ralph Lauren 在年底假日季的表现，路透社的分析师给出了营收下跌 12% 的预测。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/e-l-f-rolls-on-as-public-company-with-higher-sales-10703257/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>E.l.f. Beauty 上市之后的第一个季度财报发布 </b></a>| 美国平价化妆品牌 E.l.f. Beauty 发布了它上市之后的第一个季度财报，截止至 9 月 30 日的三个月内，季度销售额上涨 10.9%，至 5630 万美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>加拿大街头品牌 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/10/wings-and-horns-cabin-fleece-robe-2016-holiday/#slide-7\" rel=\"nofollow\">wings＋horns 发布了三款睡袍</a>，还挺潮的。这款睡袍的灵感来自于拳击运动，采用了 Fleece 面料，中间更是有棉质内里，因而有着较高的保暖性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093347wmF9yibMuPfTYWlO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110933583vd8JNIkF49PAQGc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110933584NVvloTBGxUyhwzO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110934052SbxzjmRNnhwHltC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093405Pg1aRCQb9Ockon4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093405TyPqDJSpgRkZwUXG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093412HAnxgTtDKiqaQJzd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本经典包袋品牌 Porter 最近合作新品不断。最近，它又找来了 Marni。这是自 2012 年开始，与 Marni 的第八次合作。该系列的主题是 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/marni-x-porter-surf-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Surf Collection</a>，从海边景色中汲取灵感，加以几何图形的呈现，在色彩搭配上要比之前的 Porter 丰富许多。将于 11 月 16 日在日本正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093253l9g3PxLBV4hZ7nkj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093303WAJBaOKUGmDun5wZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093315F9cw5gilJ0Vs4XKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093315Cjch63l7BYipkb2D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093315LTcMnKqJ1SzBD7Gu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093316jEtzhnHi3wOVr915.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110933154UQSgqi0cvZesMFA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093316tbxun5fGpBAXkOEe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>为庆祝 Nike 的纽约 Soho 旗舰店开业，Air Force 推出了限定配色版本。有白橙配色的，还有黑白镭射图案的版本。这个系列在美国东部时间 11 月 11 日于纽约 529 Broadway 旗舰店独家发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093039ikDlJhAzB3bqHpeK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666925\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110930492aQZtv9M5p8JV7Ko.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093102GQfNuwJ4s2K153zx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093108iXcE4Pxbfh7kr8Na.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>以艳丽的色调，花朵元素出名的日本摄影师蜷川实花，最近与东京晴空塔内的墨田水族馆合作，推出了一个<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/travel/sumida-aquarium-ninagawa-mika/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">特别展</a>。展览期间，水族馆内的水母馆会换上蜷川实花的摄影作品作为背景，配合迷离的灯光，画面还挺梦幻的。这个展从现在开始，直到 3 月 14 日结束，有兴趣的话不妨去看看。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092946mDepURG0FvJsWVEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092957o4u9B3JDnLAF6Qd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110930036Rm0QYy8TFIlWP3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093010ya2UWRhAtkswrPfM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093010JiIzDpReVPkwsbhU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093010bIhPs6mZSlfXe8io.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110930161ed34niUvjb69wgV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111093021optqS4nUF85mW6XQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>继上次 2016 年最好看的 15 双鞋之后，在线时尚杂志 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/09/sneaker-con-nyc-expensive/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Highsnobiety</a> 再次评选出了 2016 年纽约球鞋交易会 Sneaker Con New York 2016 上最贵的 15 双球鞋。都有这些：</p><div class=\"com-insert-card\">\r\n\t<div class=\"card-hd\"><p>SCNY 2016 最贵的15双鞋：</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"card-bd\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<p>1. Nike LeBron 9 “Watch the Throne” – $5,000</p><p>2. Nike Foamposite “Paranorman” – $3,000</p><p>3. Nike SB Dunk “Freddy Kreuger” – $2,000</p><p>4. adidas YEEZY Boost 350 V2 “Black/White” – $2,000</p><p>5. Air Jordan 1 “Satin” – $1,800</p><p>6. Nike Foamposite “Galaxy” – $1,600</p><p>7. Nike KD4 “Nerf” – $1,600</p><p>8. Nike Air Force 1 “Chamber of Fear” Set – $1,500</p><p>9. ASICS x Ronnie Fieg “East Coast Pack” – $1,400</p><p>10. Nike LeBron 4 “Dunkman” PE – $1,400</p><p>11. Nike Air Yeezy 1 “Net/Tan” – $1,300</p><p>12. Nike SB “What the” Dunk – $1,000</p><p>13. adidas YEEZY Boost 750 – $1,000</p><p>14. Mastermind Japan x adidas NMD XR1 – $700</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>15. ACRONYM x NikeLab Air Presto Mid – $300</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092710ZqgYp9GQbuJFHWyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092721BdMsrecpavF2wZGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110927285HIxZBcKEn97WtUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092735eMyZRVP2AgpEJUYT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110927415XxzFc6kmsup2OGv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092747rUtzqQx2fvgmO8ds.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092754o1f0c3w8kYT5btm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092801d5VawCIPTLH79XDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092807FnwxjX2Syvi6zs5J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092817mNdXPeKohafHnViI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092826di1jTQWO4oDqhr9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092832Vp4Keu2vZ1PNGQya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611110928378zQhYpcDjIr0GWgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092843hKCTxOSsz8fdDG42.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161111092849zwXRNGeM0rTQfty9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}